		  <h3>What is Fit to Print?</h3>
		  <p>This project was completed in three weeks as a part of the Insight Data Science program.</p>
		  <p>Fit to print is a tool that helps you match the writing style of your article to the editorial voice of a desired publication.</p>
		  <p>It has learned the stylistic markers of articles from 9 major publications with a variety of approaches to reporting news and compares your article to others that appeared in these publications.</p>
